thread.title: Paul Ryan Visits Border, Talk Immigration, Rides Horse
thread.title_full: Paul Ryan Visits Border, Talk Immigration, Rides Horse

author: Leigh Ann Caldwell and Suzanne Gamboa and Alex Moe
title: Paul Ryan Visits Border, Talk Immigration, Rides Horse
text: Republican Speaker of the House Paul Ryan walks to the House floor where representatives were voting on a budget resolution that is the first step in repealing the Affordable Care Act in Washington on Jan. 13, 2017. Should the measure pass, House members will begin drafting legislation to repeal President Obama's signature legislation, commonly known as Obamacare.
